    <item>
      <title>PayU Module Documentation: Log In</title>
      <link>/payu-module-documentation/getting-started/log-in.html</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Jul 2021 15:29:35 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/payu-module-documentation/getting-started/log-in.html</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;Follow the next steps to log in your PayU account.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Log into &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.payu.com&#34;&gt;www.payu.com&lt;/a&gt;, at the top right corner, you find the option to log in. For merchants in Colombia, this option is called &lt;em&gt;PayU Login&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br&gt;Alternatively, you can go directly to &lt;a href=&#34;https://merchants.payulatam.com/&#34;&gt;https://merchants.payulatam.com/&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../assets/Login1_en.png&#34; alt=&#34;PrintScreen&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Log into your PayU account by using the credentials we sent to your registered email.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../assets/Login3_en.png&#34; alt=&#34;PrintScreen&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;3&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;As soon as you log in, you can use all the available options to manage your account.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../assets/Login2_en.png&#34; alt=&#34;PrintScreen&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>PayU Module Documentation: Password Recovery</title>
      <link>/payu-module-documentation/getting-started/password-recovery.html</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Jul 2021 15:30:03 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/payu-module-documentation/getting-started/password-recovery.html</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;To recover your password, click the respective link under the &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Login&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; button.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../assets/ForgotPass_en_1.png&#34; alt=&#34;PrintScreen&#34; width=&#34;40%&#34;/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Provide the email of your account and perform the validation of the reCAPTCHA.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../assets/ForgotPass_en_2.png&#34; alt=&#34;PrintScreen&#34; width=&#34;40%&#34;/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Recover password&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;. If your email is registered, you receive an email with the password recovery URL. Check your spam box if you haven&amp;rsquo;t receive the email yet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../assets/ForgotPass_en_3.png&#34; alt=&#34;PrintScreen&#34; width=&#34;50%&#34;/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reset password&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;. A new browser window opens, provide your new password twice and click &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Set password&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../assets/ForgotPass_en_4.png&#34; alt=&#34;PrintScreen&#34; width=&#34;50%&#34;/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
